OL,3,CSchool bus driver sentenced after
OL,4,Cbeing caught watching adult content
OL,6,FA school bus driver has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto unpaid work after being caught
OL,8,Fwatching adult content while picking
OL,9,Fup pupils.
OL,11,FDavid Robe, from Ashington in
OL,12,FNorthumberland, was found guilty of
OL,13,Fwatching X-rated content while on duty.
OL,15,FThe court heard how last year between
OL,16,FMay and September children - while
OL,17,Fboarding and departing the private
OL,18,Fhire school bus between the villages
OL,19,Fof Denholm and Jedburgh - were able to
OL,20,Fsee the images over his shoulder while
OL,21,Fhe was in the driving seat.
