OL,3,CSchool bus driver sentenced after
OL,4,Cbeing caught watching adult content
OL,6,FLast month he was convicted under the
OL,7,Fcharge of breach of the peace by
OL,8,Fviewing explicit images, which he
OL,9,Fdenied.
OL,11,FAt Jedburgh Sheriff Court Sheriff
OL,12,FKevin McCarron said that while the
OL,13,Foffence met all the criteria for a
OL,14,Fcustodial sentence, he expressed
OL,15,Fconcern that the public would only
OL,16,Fhave been protected for the length of
OL,17,Fthe sentence - which would have likely
OL,18,Fbeen less than 12 months.
